{"tid":802610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★公屋戶欠租十個月 房署職員上門追租發現已化成白骨","createTime":"2018-09-01T14:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T07:34:17.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"70f5f827f262a098faa48e74aacba6c017e706b9","tid":802610,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1816857/org/c910941badab995d8e90a6cb9c842749.jpg/K4rfXquRWP4gjQlh1pGg5gbgm5Sn5HzqAYoc7wGKHO8?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1816857%2Forg%2Fc910941badab995d8e90a6cb9c842749.jpg%2FK4rfXquRWP4gjQlh1pGg5gbgm5Sn5HzqAYoc7wGKHO8%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=ed45a156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n七旬獨居老翁伏屍公屋單位無人知，直至他化成白骨，才被上門追租收樓的房署職員發現！死者居於上址十多年，有鄰居指，約在半年前，肇事單位已傳出異味，曾向大廈保安投訴，但無人報警及跟進。事件能否及早揭發？單位的門外，貼有兩封由房署發出的強遷信。住戶由欠租至被下令遷出，過程最少長達十個月。若房署及早派員上門跟進，會否早些發現事件？有區議員指，部分屋邨缺乏地區支援網絡，長者出事難以察覺，終釀成悲劇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/230130/白骨悲歌-七旬獨居翁死去無人知-揭半年前單位傳異味保安懶理\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F230130%2F%E7%99%BD%E9%AA%A8%E6%82%B2%E6%AD%8C-%E4%B8%83%E6%97%AC%E7%8D%A8%E5%B1%85%E7%BF%81%E6%AD%BB%E5%8E%BB%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E7%9F%A5-%E6%8F%AD%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%96%AE%E4%BD%8D%E5%82%B3%E7%95%B0%E5%91%B3%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E6%87%B6%E7%90%86&d=j098dpu5mEPmWltjgCn2Mxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ee20c0b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/230130/白骨悲歌-七旬獨居翁死去無人知-揭半年前單位傳異味保安懶理</a>"},{"pid":"fd4806a1e9692c9a7500c94bce753ad1b2d90c15","tid":802610,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T14:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1815158/org/e06aa8d5a7e1df48746aab173e9f5b67.jpg/VxteADL9Ch4ClOy1uR8Jj15-pgj3xjER0-GrrtPhq64?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2F